(969, 42, 0, '<h3 xss=removed><strong>Rujak Buah</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Ingredients:<br>• 1 cucumber, peeled<br>•1/4 cup brown sugar<br>• 1 mango, peeled and cubed<br>• 3 tablespoons peanuts, fried<br>• 1 papaya, cut into 1/2 inch cubes<br>• 1 hot chili peppers, seeded and sliced<br>• 1 apple tart, cut into 1/2 inch cube<br>• 1 tablespoon tamarind, dissolved in 1/4 cup of water and strained<br>• 1 pineapple, cut into 1/2 inch cubes (could use fresh or canned pineapple)</p>\r\n<p>Directions:<br>• Mix all the fruit together.<br>• Grind chilies and salt.<br>• Add brown sugar.<br>• Add fried roasted peanuts and grind completely.<br>• Pour some tamarind liquid.<br>• Mix the sauce and fruit together.<br>• Serve chilled.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>What should you do with the peanut before you grind them?</p>', 'Try Out 4', '<p>Heat into the oil.</p>', '<p>Dilute to adhesive.</p>', '<p>Set aside on the edge of the pan.</p>', '<p>Add sauce, salt, pepper powder, and sugar.</p>', '', '', '', '2', '', '1', 'main'),
