(1009, 42, 0, '<p>Dear Mr. Waskito,</p>\r\n<p>I apologize for not being able to attend your company\'s New Year Hijriyah\'s Dinner even though I had said<br>I would come. Last 23,d March, I suddenly received a telephone call at noon from my aunt in New York saying<br>that my uncle was seriously injured. So, I had to rush up to New York to see what I could. I am like a son to them<br>as they are childless. The following few days, I rushed back and forth between the hospital and my aunt\'s house<br>doing what I could for them</p>\r\n<p>I am glad to say that my uncle is out of danger now. But, he has to stay in hospital for at least three months<br>for his broken bones to mend.</p>\r\n<p>Anyhow, I hope you all had a successful dinner. Perhaps I can attend the next one.</p>\r\n<p>Yours Sincerely,<br>Subarkah</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Subarkah couldn\'t come to New Year Hijriyah\'s Dinner because . . .</p>', 'Try Out 5', '<p>he had a business in New York</p>', '<p>he had to stay in hospital in New York</p>', '<p>he had a call from his aunt to have dinner</p>', '<p>he visited his uncle who had got an accident</p>', '', '', '', '2', '', '4', 'main'),
