(1053, 42, 0, '<p><strong>Arrange the jumbled sentences into a correct paragraph.</strong></p>\r\n<p>1) Music gives us pleasure.<br>2) Music is part of every culture on Earth.<br>3) It can cheer us up, excite us, or soothe us.<br>4) Many people feel that music makes life worth living.<br>5) We can hear music on CDs and on radio or television.<br>6) We can make music ourselves if we play an instrument or sing.</p>', 'Try Out 5', '<p>1 – 6 – 5 – 2 – 3 – 4</p>', '<p>2 – 4 – 6 – 5 – 1 – 3</p>', '<p>5 – 6 – 4 – 3 – 2 – 1</p>', '<p>6 – 3 – 4 – 5 – 1 – 2</p>', '', '', '', '2', '', '2', 'main');
