(242, 242, '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">FUNGSI TEXT / FUNGSI STRING</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Fungsi text / fungsi string secara umum digunakan untuk menampilkan<u> sede</u>retan teks sebanyak&nbsp; karakter dari posisi tertentu. Table berikut menjelaskan ga fungsi text yang paling banyak digunakan yaitu:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/242/201901221451555c46cb9b07aff.png\" style=\"height:326px; width:624px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">LATIHAN KOMBINASI FUNGSI TEXT &amp; FUNGSI IF</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/242/201901221451555c46cb9b07cbe.png\" style=\"height:254px; width:624px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/242/201901221451555c46cb9b07dcd.png\" style=\"height:166px; width:436px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">LATIHAN KOMBINASI FUNGSI TEXT &amp; FUN