p;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/308/201902231030065c70be3eabf94.jpg\" style=\"height:220px; width:316px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Weld</span></span></em></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Weld</span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"> berfungsi untuk menyambung objek yang terpisah dalam mode <em>vertex. </em></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/308/201902231030065c70be3eac3e3.jpg\" style=\"height:226px; width:190px\" /></span></span></em><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/308/201902231030065c70be3eac939.jpg\" style=\"height:271px; width:388px\" /></span></span></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Align</span></span></em></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Align </span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">merupakan proses yang digunakan untuk meratakan atau mensimetriskan kedua objek pada sumbu tertentu.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/308/201902231030065c70be3ead334.png\" style=\"height:333px; width:415px\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">*</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Current Object </span></span></u></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">ialah objek yang akan dipindah.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Target Object</span></span></u></em><em> </em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">ialah objek yang menjadi target</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Smoothing</span></span></em></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Use NURMS Subdivision </span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">merupakan fasilitas yang berfungsi untuk menghaluskan objek 3D. Untuk <em>smoothing </em>objek dapat menggunakan <em>Use NURMS Subdivision </em>atau juga <em>modifier.</em></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/308/201902231030065c70be3eadddf.png\" style=\"height:396px; width:457px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n', '', '1', 0, '2019-02-23', '10:19:00', '');
