(309, 309, '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">CHAPTER 3</span></span></u></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Modelling Kemasan Box Cokelat</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/309/201902231037095c70bfe53a4fb.png\" style=\"height:340px; width:576px\" /></span></span></u></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/309/201902231037095c70bfe53cc8a.png\" style=\"height:106px; width:624px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Extrude</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Untuk memanjangkan atau menebalkan bagian tertentu pada suatu objek.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/309/201902231037095c70bfe53dadf.png\" style=\"height:273px; width:561px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Inset Polygon</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Inset Polygon</span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">,sebuah fungsi untuk membuat polygon lebih kecil atau lebih besar dari polygon yang dipilih.Ukuran baru yang dibuat dapat diatur besarnya.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/309/201902231037095c70bfe53ee1c.png\" style=\"height:216px; width:462px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Connect Edge</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Merupakan proses untuk m</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#666666\">enghubungkan <em>edge</em> dan menciptakan <em>edge</em> baru antara pasangan yang berdekatan dari <em>edge</em> yang dipilih.&nbsp;Pengaturan <em>Connect Edges</em> memungkinkan untuk menentukan jumlah <em>edge </em>baru, jumlah pemisahan satu sama lain, dan lokasinya.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/309/201902231037095c70bfe53ff66.png\" style=\"height:226px; width:568px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Soft Selection</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Soft Selction</span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"> sebuah control yang memungkinkan untuk memilih sebagian objek di sekitar pilihan eksplisit.&nbsp;Ini menyebabkan seleksi <em>eksplisit</em> berperilaku seolah-olah dikelilingi oleh &quot;medan magnet.&quot;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/309/201902231037095c70bfe541913.png\" style=\"height:222px; width:383px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Modifier Noise</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Modifier Noise</span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"> ini berfungsi untuk membuat permukaan objek menjadi bertexture secara acak. Texture yang dihasilkan pada permukaan objek terbentuk sesuai dengan setting nilai dari parameternya. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/309/201902231037095c70bfe542b2e.png\" style=\"height:346px; width:573px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">* <em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Strength </span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">: Nilai-nilai X, Y, Z harus diisi secara acak untuk menentukan besaran texture pada permukaan objeknya.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Fractal</span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"> : Harus dalam keadaan aktif bila ingin melihat efeknya.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Material Editor</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Digunakan untuk mengedit warna atau texture yang akan diterapkan</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">pada objek.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/309/201902231037095c70bfe544856.png\" style=\"height:78px; width:199px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/309/201902231037095c70bfe5453e9.png\" style=\"height:531px; width:605px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Modifier UVW MAPS</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Modifier yang berfungsi untuk mengatur pemetaan kordinat material pada suatu objek. Dengan menerapkan koordinat pemetaan pada suatu objek, pengubah Peta UVW mengontrol bagaimana materi yang dipetakan dan prosedural muncul di permukaan suatu objek.&nbsp;Memetakan koordinat menentukan bagaimana bitmap diproyeksikan ke suatu objek.&nbsp;Sistem koordinat UVW mirip dengan sistem koordinat XYZ.&nbsp;Sumbu U dan V dari bitmap sesuai dengan sumbu X dan Y.&nbsp;Sumbu W, yang sesuai dengan sumbu Z, umumnya hanya digunakan untuk peta prosedural.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/309/201902231037095c70bfe546e06.png\" style=\"height:372px; width:623px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n', '', '1', 0, '2019-02-23', '10:30:00', ''),
