(311, 311, '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">CHAPTER 5</span></span></u></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Modeling Box Makanan Ringan, Lighting, dan Rendering</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/311/201902231106205c70c6bc63b26.jpg\" style=\"height:322px; width:430px\" /></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/311/201902231106205c70c6bc64fda.png\" style=\"height:104px; width:624px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Move Setting.</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Tool Move </span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">berfungsi untuk memindah posisi objek, maupun sub objek, jadi move juga dapat digunakan untuk memindah <em>vertex, edge, polygon, border, segmen </em>dan juga dapat ditentukan jaraknya.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/311/201902231106205c70c6bc65d95.png\" style=\"height:153px; width:623px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><em>Absolute:World&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : </em></strong>Merupakan posisi atau titik pusat dari viewport 3Ds max.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><em>Offset:World&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : </em></strong>Posisi dimana letak satu objek berada.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Chamfer.</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Chamfer edge </span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">untuk membuat patahan berdasarkan <em>edge </em>yang dipilih. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Chamfer vertex </span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">untuk mengubah <em>vertex </em>menjadi bentuk segi enam atau diamond dengan menarik <em>vertex </em>tambahan.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/311/201902231106205c70c6bc66dac.png\" style=\"height:255px; width:251px\" /></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Multi/Sub-Object.</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Multi/Sub-Object memungkinkan untuk menerapkan material-material yang berbeda pada satu objek dan satu slot material. Fitur ini bermanfaat untuk menghemat slot material yang terbatas. Objek yang akan diterapkan terlebih dahulu hanya di setting IDnya pada bagian polygon.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Setting ID sub-object</span></span></u></em></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/311/201902231106205c70c6bc676c0.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:289px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Setting ID pada Polygon Objek</span></span></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Material Edior Multi/Sub-Object.</span></span></u></em></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Setelah setting ID <em>sub-object </em>selanjutnya membuat material yang akan diterapkan ke dalam objek</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/311/201902231106205c70c6bc6801d.png\" style=\"height:283px; width:470px\" /></span></span></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Discard old material</span></u></em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"> akan menghilangkan material yang sudah ada dalam slot sebelumnya.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Tampilan multi/sub-object.</span></span></u></em></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Berikut tampilan dan penjelasannya.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/311/201902231106205c70c6bc68bcd.png\" style=\"height:401px; width:301px\" /></span></span></u></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Lighting</span></span></em></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">.</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Lighting </span></span></em><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">merupakan salah satu kompenen penting dalam proses render 3D. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/311/201902231106205c70c6bc69540.png\" style=\"height:288px; width:185px\" /></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Spotlight</span></span></span></span><br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"background-color:white\">Jenis cahaya ini bentuk pencahayaannya seperti lampu sorot. Jika dianalogikan, cahaya ini sama seperti sinar lampu senter atau mobil. Penggunaan spotlight ini akan membuat pencahayaan pada sebuah objek menjadi lebih <em>focus</em>. Dan satu hal yang harus diingat bahwa penggunaan cahaya ini akan membuat area yang tidak disorot menjadi gelap.</span> <span style=\"background-color:white\">Cahaya spotlight ini dikategorikan menjadi <em>spot target</em> dan <em>spot free</em>, dimana pada <em>spot target</em> kita dapat memilih titik <em>focus</em>, tetapi tidak demikian halnya dengan <em>spot free</em>.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Direct<br />\r\n	Jenis cahaya ini pada prinsipnya sama dengan <em>spotlight</em>, tetapi antara sumber cahaya dengan sasaran cahaya memiliki intensitas cahaya yang sama.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Omni<br />\r\n	Jenis cahaya ini bentuk pencahayaannya menyebar ke segala arah dari satu titik sumber cahaya. Jika dianalogikan, cahaya ini sama seperti lampu bohlam. Pada umumnya, cahaya omni biasa digunakan pada kondisi didalam ruangan, atau sebagai pelengkap penggunaan cahaya spotlight.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Skylight<br />\r\n	Jenis cahaya ini bentuk pencahayaannya tersebar dimana-mana.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Lighting Setup</span></span></span></span></u></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#375362\"><img src=\"https://kursusonline.org/image/materi/311/201902231106205c70c6bc69bf7.png\" style=\"height:549px; width:398px\" /></span></span></span></span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:36pt; margin-right:0cm\"><span style